      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated solver with documented V&V test suite. DePuy Synthes internal SQA procedures (ISO 13485-compliant) cover model configuration management, version control, and regression testing. Software qualification records reviewed and on file."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
